  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onions and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the shio-cure potatoes and cook for 5 minutes, breaking them up with a spoon as needed.",
    "Add the semolina-rimacinata and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the shio-cure cabbage and cook until wilted, about 3 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley and a dollop of Greek yogurt if desired.",
    "Garnish with chives if available."
